text: Cass County is the name of nine counties in the United States, each named for Michigan governor, senator and presidential candidate Lewis Cass: *Cass County, Illinois *Cass County, Indiana *Cass County, Iowa *Cass County, Michigan *Cass County, Minnesota *Cass County, Missouri *Cass County, Nebraska *Cass County, North Dakota *Cass County, Texas
title: Cass County
